description: What a shame that apparently no one has video of the TV concert Something Special (Poplar Town Hall) that was broadcast at the same time as this great interview! All we get to see of that concert here is a glimpse of the beginning of Big Swing Face.
title: Buddy Rich 1967 BBC interview
